No. 10-1371. No. 10-1393. Spectrum Stores, Inc., et al., Petitioners v. Citgo Petroleum Corporation, et al. Fast Break Foods LLC, et al., Petitioners v. Saudi Arabian Oil Company, dba Saudi Aramco, et al. 565 U.S. 929, 132 S. Ct. 366,

181 L. Ed. 2d 233,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7122. October 3, 2011.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of these petitions.

Same cases below, 632 F.3d 938.
